d1: The Pie Chart titled 'UMMC COVID-19 Patient Status'.
d2: The angle of the chart represents the proportion and the colors correspond to their respective categories.

insight1.insightSentence: The pie chart shows that most of the UMMC COVID-19 patients (68.1%) are unvaccinated, followed by 13.8% of the patients who are fully vaccinated, 10.6% of the patients who have an unknown status, and 7.5% of the patients who are not eligible for vaccination.
